Am I a quiter?

Okay, so it's a couple wednesdays ago and after practice Mr. Pimlott says "I know we aren't scheduled to have practice on friday but we should have one 6-8 on friday. I'm thinking, well okay that works, I have work that day, but I can get somebody to take my shift. So I go over to Pizza Hut afterwards and look to see who isn't working - Bethany Jacobson. Okay I think, I have to call her to ask her to take my Saturday shift too anyways. So I call her about five times. Terra - our manager - kicks me out because I'm tie-ing up their phone, so I copy the phone number and go home. The next day I call her 11 times, I'm a little more frantic now. I have nobody to work for me on Friday or Saturday, and she's the only person that can take my shift. On friday we're in our 3-5 rehersal and I'm calling her like 20times. Finally I have to go up to Mr. Pimlott, MR PIMLOTT and tell him THAAT I CANT COME TO REHERSAL AHHHH WE HAVE FOUR DAYS LEFT UNTIL PREVIEWS AND I'M SKIPPING A REHERSAL??? He takes it very well and tells me that it was short notice, his fault, and told me not to worry about it....... I still feel horrible. So I'm pissed. Royaly pissed. And I still am working Saturday, and I have to till close tonight, so I won't be able to shopping for tomorrow's Hallooween party. So I find some time inbetween 9-2pm rehersal and 4-8 work and 8- whenever party to make pickle wraps, buy a constume on the day of hallooween, and everything else I need for the party AHHHHHH!!!             Yeah so I felt like quitting my job that day.

I feel like quitting choir because Miller is now Zemlin and Zemlin has always been Zemlin AND I CAN'T STAND TWO PEOPLE SAYING "Side comments are the devil!" and "Fun is not goofing in choir and laughing, it's about making good music, not haveing fun. fun is making good music." Yes making good music is fun, but all work and no play make concert choir go crazy or anybody else. Miller is an insesitve prick, who I want to tell off more that anything, watch him squirm, give him a good reason why he should not have messed with me.

Does this make me a quiter? I honestly don't know. I can't tell if it's just me being a bitch or the rest of the world.... I'm confused

While wiping up blood (bloody nose) and tears from the basement bathroom floor, I think on my father's words: "You are this close to getting kicked out of the house." I can't control my thoughts, my tears, or my blood. What did i do? I recall the last ten minutes looking for an answer. 
I walked in the door. My father comments on how i got the job at pizza hut, and then he goes on to basically tell me that the only reason why i got the job was becuase i knew everyone there. I said thanks for the compliment. He told me "It wasn't an insult you...." I went downstairs to play Daiblo. Sweet loving diablo. Where i can kill as many creatures as i want. Take out my anger. My dad comes downstairs and starts yelling at me about something. family and talking or something. He asks me if I want two people in the house (mp parents) or three (my parents and i). I wanted to scream 2. scream 2 until i was blue in the face and he was red. but i reluctantly said 3. I wanted to scream 2, and my thoughts about him. Everything he thought he is is nothing to me as i am to him. 
I stay in this prison of a bathroom. I go my upstairs bathroom. On the way i dribble blood on the hard wood floors. I'll clean it up later. I head to my bathroom, my mother doesn't accknowlegde my existence, meaning she's in on this too. I throw her a dirty look. I head to me bathroom. The only place that doesn't gave the stench of my father. 
So he wants to talk things out? Fine. But not to his face. In this journal. No, not  to his face for fear of abuse. 
I sit in the bathtub that soon starts to fill with the same bloody tears. I look around me and i see my razor. Ha, I laugh, I sound like Juliet "oh happy dagger". Yes i am juliet, but with a different source of emotions. Her's stems from undying love, mine stems from pure hatrid. Black sticky hatred. 
I recall time after time when of faults on his part. And now he wants ME to be "part of the family". Fuck him. What kind of father tells his duaghter to call someone else when she is sitting at school with a broken arm. I reasoned that he should come because he's two mins away while my mother is 15. He tells me call my mother anyhow. Call someone else because i am too busy at work. Call someone esle becuase i might get queasy. What kind of FUCKING father is that? 
I look at myself in the mirror and a red-eyed, blood-stained me. I see my weakness. I see the weak woman i have become. I i see the unaccomplished, ugly me that has no business having such good friends. And I see my faithful razor. Oh to end my life now would be a sweet rose. To not have to endure people that hurt me, like my father. To be free, free to be silent. How many times I've thought of it. jump off the boat..drive off the road...take too many pills. Yes, I've thought of it. Too much to confess to any psychaitrist.

I AM DEAF TO YOUR'S OR ANY OTHER PERSON'S LOVE.

Okay, I went to my Uncle's second wedding. He married Laura, a wicka practicer, and government spy, who just happens to be a nyphomaniac. yeah. I get there and I meet Laura and her family, not too bad, actually, pretty nice people. So I go swimming all day. Then at night, we have the rehersal dinner. We get on a shuttle bus (oh by the way this is in South Carolina) and head for oldfield. This done-up place that looks like it was built 200 years ago. And it's a golf course and such. So we go to the dinner place, where everything that we eat is basically seafood. I don't like seafood, but whatever. Then we go walking about, where we spot the ever present tree-climbing-frogs. Then we go on a pontoon boat ride where we meet up with a dolphin!!! Cool, eh?!!? He was eating the oysters.
Wedding day:
I wake up and I get ready for the wedding. Me and my mom go down to the wedding together and we open it up. There, the first thing that I see is a whole bunch of selections of Handel. I think to myself, classy woman. Then I look down, and I see that they are saying Cherokee prayers and Apache blessings. Interesting.......
Reception: (this is where it gets fuuun.....)
So following the wedding we went to the "grassy knoll". Let the drinking begin!! Well not for us kidlets of course but yes. So for the bride and grooms, the song is 'bailamos' by Enrique Eglasious. Me and my baby (9th grader, but he's still my baby cousin) cousin couldn't help but laugh. The music just got worse. So, the dancing, drinking, and seafood went on for quite a bit, untill i met Meeca (39 years old i believe), a man I wish not to meet again. He has big hands. And guys with big hands, when they put their arm around your waist, well lets just say that his hand reaches up preeeetty far. He was like hitting on me all night, and then I got to meet his wife!! He was determined to dance with me, until his wife had to haul him up to his hotel room. Wait... before he left, he told my baby cousin how to Cha-Cha, and how to get laid, and then my cousin's response was something along the lines of, i already know how to. AHHHHH!!!!!!! Then there was the wedding photographer who told me every five seconds that I would be "drop dead gorgeous" in 4-6 years. HA HA HA HA HA!!!! MIKEY WHERE ARE YOU WHEN I NEED YOU!?!?!??!?!?! Jayne
